                                        p.recipie-ingredient.pt-2.mb-0 When forming the zenkol: To avoid the dough from sticking to your hands, keep a water container next to you. Lightly dip hands into water every now and then. 
                                    li
                                        p.recipie-ingredient.pt-4.mb-0 Flour and Bulgur wheat constantly absorb water. You need to keep diluting the dough when forming it as it will harden when you are not working with it. 
                                    li
                                        p.recipie-ingredient.pt-4.mb-0 In order to make the sauce a bit thicker, Siham secretly added some flower to the browning onions.
